title: Fortios: IPSec
agents: special
catalog: network/fortigate
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the IPSec Client VPN sessions on a Fortigate firewall.
 The "fortios_ipsec_client_vpn_discovery_parameter" rule can be configured to disable this check.
 State is always "OK".


 The special agent is required for this check, 
 which can be configured via “FortiOS”.

discovery:
 One service per Client VPN configuration will be created.
